      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OLIVER DAN (7) has been competitive in stronger company of late. Kept the ball rolling last time when he led from a similar draw to this and boxed on to finish 4.3 metres from the winner in third in the Terang Cup. Ideally placed so can return to the winners' list. GHOST OF TIME (5) added to a string of wins or placings last time when second at this venue. Has the benefit of a good draw and has placed twice at this sprint trip. TRIPLE EIGHT NZ (10) draws wide but did a good job in a last-start win by 5.5 metres at this circuit. SURFINGMAKESCENTS (4) ended last campaign with a string of top-three finishes including a Group Three win when last seen six months ago and hasn't missed a place in five fresh attempts, winning twice.",
